e value and density\ndependence of the potential part and to extrapolate the total symmetry energy\nto supranuclear densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Aug 2014 19:05:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 2014 15:19:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 23 Nov 2014 16:10:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 6 Feb 2015 17:24:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-09"}
