onclude that besides phase-mixing in the magnetic field configuration, plasma\nproperties of the arcade and size of the initial pulse as well as structure of\nthe solar transition region all play a vital role in the Alfv\\'en wave\npropagation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Aug 2014 03:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
